00:06.833 --> 00:09.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
On the "NewsHour" tonight:

00:09.333 --> 00:12.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President
of the United States:
I am canceling the last
administration's completely

00:13.700 --> 00:15.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
