al-Qaida or other transnational
extremists, the way it was when

00:49.966 --> 00:51.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the 9/11 attacks
were planned there.

00:51.900 --> 00:53.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And it's Friday.

00:53.933 --> 00:58.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Mark Shields and David Brooks
analyze the latest in the
Russia investigation, the state

00:58.366 --> 01:03.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
