country, plus the rest
of the week's news.

01:03.033 --> 01:05.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
All that and more on
tonight's "PBS NewsHour."

01:05.300 --> 01:09.700 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
(BREAK)

01:09.700 --> 01:14.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: President Trump
is now apparently acknowledging
he is under investigation for

01:22.833 --> 01:25.366 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
