01:25.366 --> 01:30.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He tweeted today about
news reports that special
counsel Robert Mueller
has expanded his probe

01:31.166 --> 01:33.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
of Russian meddling
in the election.

01:33.166 --> 01:37.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The president said: "I am being
investigated for firing the
FBI director by the man who

01:39.133 --> 01:41.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
told me to fire
the FBI director."

01:41.900 --> 01:45.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That would be Deputy Attorney
General Rod Rosenstein.

01:45.366 --> 01:50.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He authored a memo criticizing
James Comey before Comey
was fired last month.

01:52.866 --> 01:56.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Rosenstein now oversees
Mueller, but several news
outlets reported today
that he, Rosenstein,

01:57.300 --> 02:00.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
may yet recuse himself.

02:00.500 --> 02:04.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Late today, the president
released his most recent
financial disclosure.

02:04.733 --> 02:08.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It covers January 2016
through this spring.

02:08.566 --> 02:11.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But it does not
list exact income.

02:11.100 --> 02:16.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It does say that he resigned
from more than 500 business
positions, many of them one day

02:16.966 --> 02:18.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
before the inauguration.

02:18.966 --> 02:23.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He listed at least $315
million in liabilities,
about the same as last year.

02:25.833 --> 02:30.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Mr. Trump spent much of this
day in Miami rolling back some
of President Obama's opening

02:31.300 --> 02:33.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
to Cuba.

02:33.366 --> 02:36.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The new policy seeks to reduce
the flow of U.S. dollars to
businesses controlled by the

02:37.566 --> 02:39.033 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Cuban military.

02:39.033 --> 02:42.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We will have a full report
later in the program.

02:42.233 --> 02:47.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In London, anger over an
apartment tower fire boiled over
today, as officials raised the

02:48.466 --> 02:52.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
death toll to 30, with
dozens still missing.

02:52.166 --> 02:55.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Jackie Long of
Independent Television
News filed this report.

02:55.900 --> 03:00.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JACKIE LONG: As the days
pass, the anger grows.

03:01.766 --> 03:03.100 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It is raw and it is visceral.

03:03.100 --> 03:05.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MAN: Shame on you!

03:05.300 --> 03:07.833 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Shame on you!

03:07.833 --> 03:11.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JACKIE LONG: This
afternoon, family and
friends of the victims and
others from across London

03:13.333 --> 03:17.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
took that anger to the local
council, storming the town hall.

03:20.633 --> 03:25.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Earlier, a more subdued
response as the queen and
duke of Cambridge visited
one of the makeshift

03:30.300 --> 03:33.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
relief centers set up in
a local sports center.

03:33.366 --> 03:36.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
They met residents
and volunteers.

03:36.133 --> 03:41.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The queen praised the bravery of
firefighters, with a desperate
father in the crowd holding

03:42.000 --> 03:43.033 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
a picture of his children.

03:43.033 --> 03:44.033 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
MAN: Please.

03:44.033 --> 03:45.033 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Come here.

03:45.033 --> 03:46.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Come here, please.

03:46.433 --> 03:48.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JACKIE LONG: The duke
promised, "I will come back."

03:48.933 --> 03:50.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MAN: I will be back.

03:50.633 --> 03:52.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I will come back.

03:52.000 --> 03:54.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I will come back.

03:54.100 --> 03:57.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JACKIE LONG: The prime
minister today announced
a five million-pound
emergency relief fund,

03:57.966 --> 04:02.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
but it wasn't enough to
assuage the anger of some.

04:02.033 --> 04:07.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Criticized yesterday for
visiting, but failing to talk to
residents, she came back today

04:09.333 --> 04:11.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and was met with this.

04:11.166 --> 04:12.900 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
WOMAN: Murderer!

04:12.900 --> 04:13.900 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Murderer!

04:13.900 --> 04:15.933 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Murderer!

04:15.933 --> 04:19.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JACKIE LONG: Also today, in
a recent statement, the prime
minister assured residents that

04:21.300 --> 04:24.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the government is there for all
the victims of this tragedy.

04:24.766 --> 04:28.166 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Jackie Long of
Independent Television News.

04:28.166 --> 04:32.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Guardian newspaper reported
today that renovations to
the apartment tower used a

04:32.933 --> 04:37.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
cheaper exterior paneling,
instead of a flame-resistant
version that's more expensive.

04:39.866 --> 04:44.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Iran's supreme leader, Ayatollah
Ali Khamenei, is charging
that new sanctions approved by

04:45.700 --> 04:48.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the U.S. Senate violate
the 2015 nuclear deal.

04:48.466 --> 04:51.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The sanctions are aimed at
Tehran's missile program.

04:51.333 --> 04:56.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Today, a senior adviser
to Khamenei said they
are unquestionably a
breach of both the spirit

04:57.466 --> 04:59.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
and the letter of the
nuclear agreement.

04:59.933 --> 05:04.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
The spokesman promised
that Iran will respond.

05:04.000 --> 05:09.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Russia's military says that
it may have killed Abu Bakr
al-Baghdadi, the Islamic State's

05:09.800 --> 05:11.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
leader, in an airstrike.

05:11.866 --> 05:16.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Defense Ministry in Moscow
said today the strike happened
late last month in Syria.

05:17.733 --> 05:19.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It said it is still
verifying the claim.

05:19.600 --> 05:23.966 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
U.S. officials say they have
seen no evidence that it's true.

05:23.966 --> 05:28.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The U.N. Refugee Agency warned
today that 100,000 Iraqi
civilians remain trapped behind

05:30.133 --> 05:32.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Islamic State lines
in Western Mosul.

05:32.966 --> 05:37.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
The officials say that
ISIS militants are
using the civilians as
human shields, as they

05:37.800 --> 05:39.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
continue to lose ground.

05:39.766 --> 05:41.800 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
The announcement came in Geneva.

05:41.800 --> 05:46.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN: If you put yourself in
their situation, you know, when
you may have a fighter on top

05:48.233 --> 05:51.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of your roof, attracting the
artillery fire, you can imagine
in which condition of penury

05:53.800 --> 05:58.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and panic they live, being
unable to flee and knowing
that, if they try to flee, if

06:00.733 --> 06:02.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
they are caught,
they will be killed.

06:02.900 --> 06:07.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Iraqi government
forces have been fighting to
retake Mosul since October.

06:09.933 --> 06:13.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Back in this country,
a Massachusetts woman
was convicted today of
involuntary manslaughter

06:14.333 --> 06:16.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
for urging her boyfriend
to commit suicide.

06:16.566 --> 06:21.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Michelle Carter sent hundreds
of text messages to Conrad Roy.

06:21.333 --> 06:26.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
In July of 2014, Roy
filled his truck with
deadly carbon monoxide,
then got out, contacted

06:28.433 --> 06:30.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Carter, and told
her he was scared.

06:30.633 --> 06:33.000 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
She responded: "Get back in."

06:33.000 --> 06:36.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
She could get as much
as 20 years in prison.

06:36.900 --> 06:41.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Doctors in Washington now
say that Representative
Steve Scalise can hope
to make a full recovery

06:42.766 --> 06:44.800 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
after being shot this week.

06:44.800 --> 06:49.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
He was gravely wounded
when a gunman opened
fire at a congressional
Republican baseball

06:49.666 --> 06:51.766 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
practice.

06:51.766 --> 06:55.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Scalise is still in critical
condition, and is expected
to have additional surgery.

06:57.033 --> 07:00.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
On Wall Street today, the Dow
Jones industrial average gained
24 points to close at 21384.

07:01.633 --> 07:06.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The Nasdaq fell 13 points, and
the S&amp;P 500 added a fraction.

07:07.966 --> 07:11.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
For the week, the Dow
and the S&amp;P rose a
fraction of a percent.

07:11.033 --> 07:14.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
The Nasdaq fell
nearly 1 percent.

07:14.400 --> 07:19.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The man who brought about
Germany's reunification,
Helmut Kohl, died today.

07:19.200 --> 07:24.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He became chancellor of West
Germany in 1982 and guided the
rejoining with East Germany

07:25.600 --> 07:29.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
after the Berlin Wall fell
and the Soviet Bloc collapsed.

07:29.200 --> 07:33.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Helmut Kohl ultimately served
as chancellor for 16 years.

07:33.333 --> 07:36.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
He was 87 years old.

07:36.033 --> 07:41.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And Los Angeles temporarily
turned into Gotham City
last night in memory
of Adam West, who

07:42.200 --> 07:44.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
played Batman on
the 1960s TV show.

07:44.766 --> 07:49.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hundreds of fans gathered
to watch as officials
flipped a switch and
flashed the iconic Bat

07:50.566 --> 07:52.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Signal on city hall.

07:52.766 --> 07:56.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Adam West died this
week at the age of 88.

07:56.366 --> 08:00.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Still to come on the "NewsHour":
my conversation with former
General David Petraeus on the

08:00.100 --> 08:05.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
fight in Afghanistan; new
travel and business restrictions
between the U.S. and Cuba; and

08:13.933 --> 08:18.466 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
much more.

08:18.466 --> 08:23.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Wars in Afghanistan, Syria, and
Iraq, tensions within the Gulf
states, and a new administration

08:25.433 --> 08:29.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
trying to manage an exploding
region, all topics for retired
General David Petraeus.

08:31.433 --> 08:35.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He commanded American and
coalition forces in the wars in
Iraq and Afghanistan, and served

08:36.933 --> 08:40.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
as overall commander of
U.S. military operations
in the Middle East.

08:40.533 --> 08:44.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He later served as director
of the CIA in 2011 and 2012.

08:44.233 --> 08:47.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He's now with a global
investment firm.

08:47.200 --> 08:49.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We spoke a short time ago.

08:49.266 --> 08:53.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I started by asking him
about reports that the Trump
administration will soon send

08:53.266 --> 08:58.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
4,000 additional U.S. troops
to Afghanistan, and whether
he thinks it is a smart move.

08:59.100 --> 09:01.633 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GEN.

09:01.633 --> 09:03.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID PETRAEUS (RET.),
Former Commander, U.S.
Central Command: I think
it is, and it's heartening.

09:03.633 --> 09:06.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think what we need to get to
in Afghanistan is a sustainable,
measuring the expenditure

09:08.300 --> 09:11.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
of blood and treasure,
a sustainable,
sustained commitment.

09:11.533 --> 09:15.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We need to recognize that we
went there for a reason and we
stayed for a reason, to ensure

09:15.733 --> 09:20.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that Afghanistan is not
once again a sanctuary
for al-Qaida or other
transnational extremists,

09:20.533 --> 09:24.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the way it was when the 9/11
attacks were planned there.

09:24.100 --> 09:26.000 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
That's why we need to stay.

09:26.000 --> 09:30.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We also have a very useful
platform there for the regional
counterterrorist effort.

09:30.566 --> 09:34.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, of course, we have greatly
reduced the capabilities of
al-Qaida's senior leaders

09:34.766 --> 09:38.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in that region, including,
of course, taking
out Osama bin Laden.

09:38.866 --> 09:40.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But this is a
generational struggle.

09:40.733 --> 09:43.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This is not something that is
going to be won in a few years.

09:43.833 --> 09:46.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're not going to take
a hill, plant a flag, go
home to a victory parade.

09:46.966 --> 09:51.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we need to be there for
the long haul, but in a way
that is, again, sustainable.

09:51.200 --> 09:56.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have been in Korea
for 65-plus years because
there is an important
national interest for

09:57.400 --> 09:59.433 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
that.

09:59.433 --> 10:01.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We were in Europe for a very
long period of time, still
there, of course, and actually

10:01.966 --> 10:06.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
with a renewed emphasis
now, given Russia's
aggressive actions.

10:06.300 --> 10:08.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I think that's the way
we need to approach this.

10:08.400 --> 10:10.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Now, to be sure, the forces...

10:10.300 --> 10:12.300 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

10:12.300 --> 10:14.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Are you
saying we may need to stay in
Afghanistan 60, 70, 80 years?

10:14.466 --> 10:16.500 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GEN.

10:16.500 --> 10:19.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID PETRAEUS: I wouldn't say
60, but I think we shouldn't
approach this as a year-on-year

10:19.733 --> 10:20.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
mission.

10:20.966 --> 10:22.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I think that was
actually harmful.

10:22.966 --> 10:26.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think it gave all of the
Afghan leaders and so forth were
-- basically get the jitters.

10:28.800 --> 10:32.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Those who are investing money
consider every year whether
to keep it there or whether to

